headline: J. M. Smucker (SJM): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q4 Earnings?
summary: J. M. Smucker currently trades at $116.01 per share and has shown little upside over the past six months, posting a small loss of 1.9%. However, the stock is beating the S&P 500’s 7.3% decline during that period.
